OL,3,CNI first in UK to introduce graduated
OL,4,Cdriving licences
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland is to become the
OL,7,Ffirst part of the UK to introduce
OL,8,Fadditional restrictions for new
OL,9,Fdrivers.
OL,11,FThe proposals to introduce graduated
OL,12,Fdriver licensing (GDL) in October 2026
OL,13,Fhave been described by Stormont's
OL,14,FInfrastructure Minister Liz Kimmins as
OL,15,Fthe "most significant reform to driver
OL,16,Flicensing and testing in almost 70
OL,17,Fyears".
