OL,3,CNI first in UK to introduce graduated
OL,4,Cdriving licences
OL,6,FGDL is a road safety scheme designed
OL,7,Fto reduce the disproportionate
OL,8,Finvolvement of new and young drivers
OL,9,Fin serious collisions.
OL,11,FThe plans include the introduction of
OL,12,Fa revised training, testing and post-
OL,13,Ftest framework for new drivers and
OL,14,Fmotorcyclists.
OL,16,FThe proposals include:
OL,18,F` A mandatory minimum learning period
OL,19,Fof six months before a learner driver
OL,20,Fcan undertake their practical driving
OL,21,Ftest.
