OL,3,CNI first in UK to introduce graduated
OL,4,Cdriving licences
OL,6,F` A programme of training which must
OL,7,Fbe completed and recorded in a logbook
OL,8,Fbefore a learner driver can undertake
OL,9,Ftheir practical driving test
OL,11,F` An increase in the restriction
OL,12,Fperiod from the current 12 months to
OL,13,F24 months, requiring new drivers to
OL,14,Fdisplay a plate on the vehicle for two
OL,15,Fyears after receiving a full licence
OL,17,F` A period of six months with night-
OL,18,Ftime driving restrictions for new
OL,19,Fdrivers under 24
