OL,3,CNI first in UK to introduce graduated
OL,4,Cdriving licences
OL,6,F` Age-related night-time passenger
OL,7,Frestrictions for newly qualified
OL,8,Fdrivers, with exemption for immediate
OL,9,Ffamily members.
OL,11,FGDL permits 'L' drivers to drive on a
OL,12,Fmotorway as long as they are
OL,13,Faccompanied by a driving instructor.
OL,14,FOnce the learner passes their test,
OL,15,Fthey will be issued with the new 'R'
OL,16,Fplate which also allows them to drive
OL,17,Fon a motorway, where they can drive up
OL,18,Fto the speed limit.
OL,20,FIn 2025, 56 people were killed in road
OL,21,Ftraffic collisions in Northern Ireland.
