OL,3,CNI first in UK to introduce graduated
OL,4,Cdriving licences
OL,6,FMs Kimmins said: "I am announcing the
OL,7,Fmost significant reform to driver
OL,8,Flicensing and testing in almost 70
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,F"These changes are aimed at young
OL,12,Fdrivers who are sadly most likely to
OL,13,Fbe killed or seriously injured on our
OL,14,Froads.
OL,16,F"In 2024, there were 164 casualties
OL,17,F(killed or seriously injured) from
OL,18,Fcollisions where a car driver aged 17-
OL,19,F23 was responsible.
