OL,3,CNI first in UK to introduce graduated
OL,4,Cdriving licences
OL,6,F"This age group of drivers accounts
OL,7,Ffor 24% of fatal or serious collisions
OL,8,Fdespite holding just 8% of licences."
OL,10,FThe minister said the objective was to
OL,11,Fcreate drivers who are safe.
OL,13,FShe added: "The introduction of GDL
OL,14,Fplans to achieve this through a
OL,15,Fstructured approach to learning to
OL,16,Fdrive, including the completion of a
OL,17,Fprogramme of training and logbook.
