OL,3,CNI first in UK to introduce graduated
OL,4,Cdriving licences
OL,6,F"This will better prepare drivers for
OL,7,Fboth the driving test and initial post-
OL,8,Ftest driving period by helping
OL,9,Flearners understand how human factors
OL,10,Fsuch as their attitude, personality,
OL,11,Fbehaviour and feelings affect their
OL,12,Fdriving style.
OL,14,F"Road safety is a priority, and GDL
OL,15,Fwill be a valuable tool to help me
OL,16,Fensure everyone who uses our roads
OL,17,Fdoes so safely."
OL,19,FA public safety campaign will shortly
OL,20,Fbe launched ahead of the proposals
OL,21,Fbeing introduced on October 1 2026.
